data.description: Welcome to your cozy starter home in a quiet New Hope neighborhood, just a stroll away from Northwood Park. Inside, you'll love the updates sprinkled throughout. Gorgeous hardwood floors, fun light fixtures plus stainless steel kitchen appliances really make the place pop. Head down to the family room and you'll find it's just the spot to chill, thanks to comfy LVP flooring, a cool shiplap wall, and big windows that let in loads of sunshine. Out back, there's a deck that's perfect for BBQs, surrounded by big trees for that just-right mix of sun and shade. Plus, there’s a firepit for nights under the stars and a handy shed for all your extra stuff.  ** Showings cut off Saturday 7pm and offer deadline Sunday 10am **
